[As amended June 2014]

Schedule 2, Section V: Except as the Bank shall otherwise agree, the Borrower shall take, in consultation with the Guarantor, allactions necessary to ensure that its Cumulative Debt to Equity shall be lower than 4.5 by closing of each fiscal year duringProject implementation. [As amended June 2014]
